the world to him.

12:17.570 --> 12:19.003
No, I'm gonna
go with my thing.

12:19.005 --> 12:22.140
Adult adam:
<i>As my dad was putting</i>
<i>his plan into motion,</i>

12:22.142 --> 12:25.310
<i>I was praying erica was,</i>
<i>as well.</i>

12:26.011 --> 12:27.078
Oh, balls.

12:27.080 --> 12:30.281
Hey, boopie.
Look what mama bought.

