12:35.856 --> 12:38.757
I'm wearing the pants.
Don't wear the pants.

12:38.759 --> 12:39.591
Hey, mom?

12:39.593 --> 12:40.291
Oh, look, it's erica.

12:40.293 --> 12:43.628
Check out this box of
old photos that I found
in the basement.

12:43.630 --> 12:44.729
Man, such good memories.

12:44.731 --> 12:48.566
