I'm kind of losing interest.

13:08.488 --> 13:11.256
Oh, no, no.
Don't lose interest.

13:11.258 --> 13:13.324
Um... I can do both.

13:13.326 --> 13:15.160
Adam, I'll meet you
at the dance.

13:15.162 --> 13:15.794
Erica, don't move.

13:15.796 --> 13:19.631
I'm just gonna
run upstairs and get
my smock and glue gun.

13:21.467 --> 13:23.201
There's 1,000 pictures
in this box.

13:23.203 --> 13:25.436
There's no way she's gonna
make it to that dance.

13:25.438 --> 13:27.605
Have I mentioned
that I love you?

13:27.607 --> 13:30.241
Say it one more time,
and I won't help you.

13:30.243 --> 13:32.010
Adult adam:  <i>Erica had</i>
<i>actually pulled it off.</i>

13:32.012 --> 13:35.013
<i>My mom was gonna be</i>
<i>stuck home all night!</i>

13:35.015 --> 13:36.614
All right,
got our cocoa.

13:36.616 --> 13:39.050
Let's cozy up
and spend the next few hours

13:39.052 --> 13:41.820
