my entire life.

13:41.954 --> 13:44.522
And...Done!

13:44.524 --> 13:46.825
What?
How did you do this?

13:46.827 --> 13:48.092
Please, I've had
this whole thing

13:48.094 --> 13:50.228
Mapped out in my mind
for years.

13:50.230 --> 13:52.597
You pressed flowers...

13:52.599 --> 13:56.234
And put
my favorite music lyrics
beneath each photo.

13:56.236 --> 13:59.037
Take some time with it.
(chuckles)

13:59.039 --> 14:01.406
It's like a beautiful
kaleidoscope of my life.

14:01.408 --> 14:02.774
(chuckles)
yeah, touching stuff.

14:02.776 --> 14:04.676
Now, I've got to get
to that dance.

14:04.678 --> 14:06.578
The jam's not gonna
pump itself up. (chuckles)

14:06.580 --> 14:08.479
Adult adam:  <i>While erica's</i>
<i>plan had failed,</i>

14:08.481 --> 14:11.182
<i>My dad was giving his</i>
<i>one more shot.</i>

14:11.184 --> 14:13.751
Hey, uh, bar,
you got a sec?

14:13.753 --> 14:18.423
I think we should have a talk,
man to man.

14:18.425 --> 14:20.258
Really? Okay.

14:20.260 --> 14:22.560
I've never been
a great communicator,

14:22.562 --> 14:27.699
So I think I should
keep things as direct
and exact as possible.

14:27.701 --> 14:31.603
All right.
So, we're not just gonna
have the talk.

14:31.605 --> 14:33.872
We're gonna
experience the talk.

14:33.874 --> 14:35.240
We're gonna do
some role-playing.

14:35.242 --> 14:37.175
I'm gonna be the girl.
You'll be the boy.

14:37.177 --> 14:40.812
And we're gonna learn
where babies come from
with our hands.

14:40.814 --> 14:42.680
Take a fraggle.
I don't want the fraggle.

14:42.682 --> 14:44.482
(high-pitched voice)
I'm a pretty fraggle girl.

14:44.484 --> 14:47.418
Would you like to come up
to my condo for a nightcap?

14:47.420 --> 14:52.891
