since I put myself
through nursing school.

14:52.893 --> 14:54.192
Fraggles don't own condos!

14:54.194 --> 14:56.895
Take it.
Put your hand in the fraggle.

14:56.897 --> 14:58.730
Keep the fraggle
away from me!

14:58.732 --> 15:02.467
Take it now!
Stop it!
I was messing with you!

15:02.469 --> 15:03.635
I know everything, okay?

15:03.637 --> 15:05.236
I know
you know everything.

15:05.238 --> 15:07.138
Then why
are you torturing me?

15:07.140 --> 15:08.740
Because you tortured me!

15:08.742 --> 15:10.375
What kind of moron
makes their dad

15:10.377 --> 15:12.977
Give them the talk
when they don't need the talk?

15:12.979 --> 15:14.979
Who does that?
Me.

15:14.981 --> 15:16.481
And you know why?

15:16.483 --> 15:17.515
'cause you couldn't
be bothered

15:17.517 --> 15:19.651
To have the talk
when I actually needed it.

15:19.653 --> 15:21.853
Dads are supposed
to teach their kids stuff...

15:21.855 --> 15:26.724
How to throw a fastball
and change a tire and shave.

15:26.726 --> 15:28.092
You never
taught me anything.

15:28.094 --> 15:30.795
In my defense,
I know very little.

15:30.797 --> 15:34.565
And fraggles,
they can't be nurses.

15:34.567 --> 15:37.135
They dance
their cares away.

15:37.536 --> 15:39.337
Adult adam:  <i>As my dad</i>
<i>was striking out at home,</i>

15:39.339 --> 15:41.806
<i>I was ready to hit</i>
<i>the dance floor at school.</i>

15:41.808 --> 15:45.076
<i>The only problem was</i>
<i>that at a junior-high dance,</i>

15:45.078 --> 15:47.612
<i>Kids don't dance,</i>
<i>but that didn't matter.</i>

15:47.614 --> 15:49.614
<i>With my mom distracted</i>
<i>by erica at home,</i>

15:49.616 --> 15:54.819
<i>It was time for me</i>
<i>to show dana</i>
<i>my awesome moves.</i>

15:54.821 --> 15:57.088
May I have this dance?
(laughs)

15:57.090 --> 15:59.157
Kidding, I'm just
here to chaperone.

15:59.159 --> 16:01.092
Unless you're bored.
Then let's boogie.

16:01.094 --> 16:03.361
(gasps)
what are you doing here?

16:03.363 --> 16:04.329
I told you I'd make it.

16:04.331 --> 16:05.930
Now I'm gonna
need you to leave.

16:05.932 --> 16:06.664
Will you stop with that?

16:06.666 --> 16:09.367
I really want to be here
at this dance.

16:09.369 --> 16:12.103
You can't deny me
that pleasure, adam.

16:12.105 --> 16:12.904
Go away!

16:12.906 --> 16:17.008
But you're the one
who asked me to
teach you how to dance.

16:17.010 --> 16:17.775
It was a mistake.

16:17.777 --> 16:20.111
I asked for your help
in a moment of weakness.

16:20.113 --> 16:21.879
It'll never happen again.

16:22.081 --> 16:25.783
Okay. I guess
I'll just go then.

16:25.785 --> 16:26.718
(swishing)

16:26.720 --> 16:30.455
Adult adam:
<i>The sound of those swishing</i>
<i>parachute pants running away</i>

16:30.457 --> 16:31.823
<i>Was the sound of victory.</i>

16:31.825 --> 16:34.892
<i>So, then,</i>
<i>why did I feel so bad?</i>

16:36.395 --> 16:40.031
<i>Even though I was forced</i>
<i>to hurt my mom</i>
<i>in the name of love,</i>

16:40.033 --> 16:41.165
<i>I had to forge on.</i>

16:41.167 --> 16:43.835
<i>I'd charm dana</i>
<i>with a cup of hawaiian punch</i>

16:43.837 --> 16:45.536
<i>And then make my move.</i>

16:45.538 --> 16:46.804
Dana.
(panting) hey.

16:46.806 --> 16:48.506
Want some punch?
No, I'm just gonna go

16:48.508 --> 16:52.010
Hang outside until my mom
dances herself out.

16:52.012 --> 16:54.078
I didn't know
your mom was a chaperone.

16:54.080 --> 16:55.713
Yeah, and she went out
for margaritas

16:55.715 --> 16:57.582
With the other moms
before the dance.

16:57.584 --> 16:59.951
It's so humiliating.

17:00.419 --> 17:03.021
Adult adam:  <i>Turns out,</i>
<i>my mom was right</i>
<i>about one thing...</i>

17:03.023 --> 17:06.057
<i>Every kid is embarrassed</i>
<i>by their parents.</i>
<i>Mom!</i>

17:06.059 --> 17:08.159
<i>And it gave me an idea.</i>
<i>Mom!</i>

17:08.161 --> 17:10.895
Don't worry.
I'm just leaving.

17:10.897 --> 17:12.764
No. I need your help.

17:12.766 --> 17:14.232
Oh, no.
You don't get my help.

17:14.234 --> 17:17.068
Not after you said
you're never gonna
ask for it again.

17:17.070 --> 17:18.636
That's not how this works.

17:18.638 --> 17:19.670
I'm sorry, okay?

17:19.672 --> 17:21.672
Sometimes,
I need your help.

17:21.674 --> 17:25.443
But sometimes,
I just want you gone.

17:25.445 --> 17:26.711
Well, that's confusing!

17:26.713 --> 17:28.813
I know.
It makes no sense.

17:28.815 --> 17:31.883
But for now,
that's just how it's gonna be.

17:31.885 --> 17:32.717
So, what do you want?

17:32.719 --> 17:34.886
I want you to go
on that dance floor

17:34.888 --> 17:38.056
And just be yourself.

17:39.158 --> 17:40.124
I can do that.

17:40.126 --> 17:41.626
<i>♪ we can dance if we want to</i>

17:41.628 --> 17:44.028
<i>♪ we can leave</i>
<i>your friends behind</i>

17:44.030 --> 17:46.264
<i>♪ 'cause your friends don't</i>
<i>dance, and if they don't dance</i>

17:46.266 --> 17:48.966
<i>♪ well,</i>
<i>they're no friends of mine</i>

17:48.968 --> 17:51.035
<i>♪ say, we can go</i>
<i>where we want to</i>

17:51.037 --> 17:53.237
<i>♪ a place where</i>
<i>they will never find</i>

17:53.239 --> 17:55.740
<i>♪ and we can act like we come</i>
<i>from out of this world</i>

17:55.742 --> 17:57.542
<i>♪ leave the real one</i>
<i>far behind</i>

17:57.544 --> 17:58.676
Well, what do you know?

17:58.678 --> 18:01.045
No one's looking
at your mom anymore.

18:01.047 --> 18:01.913
Did you do that for me?

18:01.915 --> 18:05.183
Well, I definitely
didn't do it for me.

18:08.287 --> 18:10.054
<i>♪ we can go</i>
<i>where we want to</i>

18:10.056 --> 18:11.155
<i>♪ the night is young,</i>
<i>and so am I</i>

18:11.157 --> 18:12.824
Adult adam:
<i>My plan had worked.</i>

18:12.826 --> 18:13.458
<i>I'd saved dana,</i>

18:13.460 --> 18:16.294
<i>But I couldn't have predicted</i>
<i>what happened next.</i>

18:16.296 --> 18:18.396
<i>My mom actually got</i>

18:18.398 --> 18:21.265
<i>Junior-high-school kids</i>
<i>to dance...</i>

18:21.267 --> 18:22.500
<i>And it was epic.</i>

18:22.502 --> 18:24.435
<i>♪ and you can act real rude</i>
<i>and totally removed</i>

18:24.437 --> 18:26.337
<i>♪ and I can act</i>
<i>like an imbecile</i>

18:26.339 --> 18:29.474
<i>♪ say, we can dance,</i>
<i>we can dance</i>

18:29.476 --> 18:32.110
<i>♪ everything's</i>
<i>out of control ♪</i>

18:32.112 --> 18:36.447
(slow ballad playing)

18:36.548 --> 18:37.815
Come on!
I like the fast ones!

18:37.817 --> 18:40.618
You know what?
I'm gonna go out
and get some fresh air.

18:40.620 --> 18:42.420
Why don't you come with me?

18:42.821 --> 18:43.354
Have fun, baby.

18:43.356 --> 18:47.558
Adult adam:
<i>Normally, we don't say</i>
<i>"I love you" in our family.</i>

18:47.560 --> 18:51.395
<i>Luckily for me,</i>
<i>my mom could read lips.</i>

18:51.397 --> 18:54.732
<i>♪ I was always reachin'</i>

18:55.067 --> 18:59.303
<i>♪ you were just a girl I knew</i>

18:59.305 --> 19:05.276
<i>♪ I took for granted</i>
<i>the friend I have in you</i>

19:05.278 --> 19:06.644
Want some company?

19:06.646 --> 19:08.579
