19:10.949 --> 19:11.549
(sighs)

19:11.551 --> 19:13.684
I don't even know
how to talk to my kids.

19:13.686 --> 19:14.418
I'm aware.

19:14.420 --> 19:16.120
I always thought
that I would do

19:16.122 --> 19:18.556
Everything different
than my dad did.

19:18.558 --> 19:20.258
